## Epic 8: Financial Management

### Story 01 – Rule-Based Payments for Activities

**User Story:** As a Finance Manager, I want payments to be automatically generated based on predefined rules so that investigator payments are accurate, timely, and compliant with study terms.
**Detailed Description:** System should automatically generate payment line items when activities occur — for example, completion of a subject visit, site activation, or meeting enrollment milestones. Payment rules may include conditions, multipliers, caps, and currency preferences. Each generated payment must link to triggering activity and appear in the site financial ledger.
